snippet.title: C64 Game - Rescue Squad
snippet.description:
Short but fun fire-fighting game from the creators of the (original) Castle Wolfenstein and Space Taxi. Repeats and increases in difficulty after level 3.

1983, Muse Software  
Musician: Silas S. Warner  
Programmer: John F. Kutcher
